          Built using <strong>Node.js</strong>, <strong>Express</strong>, <strong>EJS</strong>, and <strong>PostgreSQL</strong>,
          TripSync brings together creativity and logic ‚Äî turning wanderlust into interactive, real-world adventures.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
